  "identifier": "SB 172",
  "title": "AN ACT relating to utility fuel adjustment and declaring an emergency.",
  "abstract": "Amend KRS 278.277 to permit the Public Service Commission to allow, upon the request of an electric utility, an extension of the period for recovery of an electric utility's fuel adjustment costs to reduce volatility for consumers and encourage stability in rates.",
